"\n"
" Add a new host:\n"
"   ipa host-add --location=\"3rd floor lab\" --locality=Dallas "
"test.example.com\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
" Adicionar uma nova máquina:\n"
"   ipa host-add --location=\"3rd floor lab\" --"
"locality=Dallastest.example.com\n"

